To get going quickly with the stand-alone version:

1) install ruby
	- On Fedora and RHEL: "yum install -y ruby"
	- On *buntu: "apt-get install -y ruby"
2) run ./thehat-installer
3) run ./thehat-tty example.ini


Please go to https://github.com/svdasein/thehat/wiki/Configuration for
complete installation instructions.
